---
/* Global Edge Component - Multilingual Mastery */
---
<section id="advantage" class="global-advantage">
    <div class="advantage-header">
        <h2 class="text-gradient">The Multilingual Mastery</h2>
        <p>Ontario isn't just one market. It’s a global intersection.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="language-showcase">
        <div class="lang-card">
            <span class="lang-label">English</span>
            <h3>Universal Reach</h3>
            <p>High-conversion SEO and clean, authoritative copy for a global audience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lang-card highlight">
            <span class="lang-label">Tamil | தமிழ்</span>
            <h3>Community Authority</h3>
            <p>Native architecture for the South Asian market, ensuring cultural nuance and local trust.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lang-card highlight-mandarin">
            <span class="lang-label">Mandarin | 普通话</span>
            <h3>Global Investment</h3>
            <p>Bridging the gap for international investors and Ontario's largest professional networks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lang-card">
            <span class="lang-label">Spanish | Español</span>
            <h3>Expanding Markets</h3>
            <p>Tapping into the fastest-growing professional networks in North America.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p class="edge-note">
        We don't just translate words; we <strong>architect native experiences</strong>. Our platforms use intelligent language toggling to serve the right content to the right lead.
    </p>
</section>

<style>
    .global-advantage { 
        padding: 8rem 1.5rem; 
        text-align: center; 
        max-width: 1200px; 
        margin: 0 auto; 
        background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.02); 
        border-radius: 40px; 
    }
    
    .text-gradient { 
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #34d399, #a3e635); 
        -webkit-background-clip: text; 
        background-clip: text; 
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; 
        color: #34d399; 
    }

    .advantage-header h2 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #fff; }
    
    .language-showcase { 
        display: grid; 
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); 
        gap: 1.5rem; 
        margin: 4rem 0; 
    }

    .lang-card { 
        padding: 3rem 2rem; 
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); 
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); 
        border-radius: 24px; 
        text-align: left; 
        transition: 0.3s; 
    }

    .lang-card.highlight { 
        border-color: #fbbf24; 
        background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.03); 
    }

    .lang-card.highlight-mandarin { 
        border-color: #ef4444; 
        background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.03); 
    }

    .lang-label { 
        color: #fbbf24; 
        font-weight: 800; 
        font-size: 0.8rem; 
        text-transform: uppercase; 
        letter-spacing: 2px; 
    }

    .highlight-mandarin .lang-label { color: #ef4444; }
    
    .lang-card h3 { margin: 1rem 0; font-size: 1.5rem; color: #fff; }
    
    .lang-card p { color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; }

    .edge-note { 
        max-width: 800px; 
        margin: 3rem auto 0; 
        font-size: 1.1rem; 
        color: #cbd5e1;
        line-height: 1.6; 
    }
    
    strong { color: #34d399; }
</style>